    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "SAIL_MPROC protocol"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "From the SAIL perspective, The SAIL_MPROC protocol for multicore signaling and COMPUTE_L1 (as of ES9) for signaling between the SAIL and MD (that is, external mailbox) is enabled"
    },
